            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> diced onion</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
