          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop any larger pieces of <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
