    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped meat-free chick'n</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-6 min or until it's browned</p><p>Tip: Add an extra knob of butter if the meat-free chick'n is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 6,
