        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free chick'n is browned, add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>ground almonds</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2-4 min or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Once done, stir in your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and cook for a further 1 min or until it's warmed through – this is your<strong> mild meat-free chick'n korma</strong></p>",
